Class PluginGuiListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dukascopy.api.plugins.PluginGuiListener

  • public abstract class PluginGuiListener
extends java.lang.Object
    Listener for plugin actions to be used from JForex-SDK, where the API user has to:
    • provide the widget and menu item container of his own,
    • handle listener adding/removal.
